                            <comment id="17574495" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2022 05:25:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For beans you need to bind them to the registry to be shared and available in Camel&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
@org.apache.camel.BindToRegistry(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;helloBean&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;HelloBean {

    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; greeting() {
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Hello!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then you can use it from other DSLs such as yaml&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# camel-k: language=yaml

# Write your routes here, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; example:
- from:
    uri: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;timer:yaml&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
    parameters:
      period: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;1000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
    steps:
      - bean: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;helloBean&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
      - log: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${body}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17574497" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2022 05:34:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I updated the camel-jbang documentation about this&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17574636" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2022 09:47:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I found a way to improve camel joor (java dsl) to make classloading available outside as well, so your example runs OOTB in next releases&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-18339&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-18339&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
